These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, firefighter, teacher, entrepreneur
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the firefighter##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the scientist##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the teacher##1
12. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Job         | firefighter  | entrepreneur    | scientist       | teacher     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

